### OpenCRE (Common Requirements Enumeration)

- Purpose:
Solves the mapping problem across different security standards.
Provides a common language to compare security frameworks.
- Functionality:
Maps security standards to Common Requirements (CREs).
Makes it easier to find related requirements across frameworks.
Improves shared understanding and maintains links between standards.

